        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "A PROLOGUE",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "People in London-not merely literary folk, but even those \"higher social circles\" to which a certain publisher, whose name-or race-it is hardly fair to mention, had so obsequiously climbed-often wondered whence had come the wealth that enabled him to maintain such an establishment, give such elaborate \"parties,\" have so many automobiles, and generally make all that display which is so convincing to the modern mind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "There is only one democracy, and that is controlled by gentlemen with names that hardly sound beautiful enough to mention in fairy tales-that democracy of money to which the fairest flower of our aristocracy now bows her coroneted head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Therefore, all sorts of distinguished and beautiful people came to the publisher's \"parties.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Aristocrats in London, of course, know nothing of a northern district of New York City called Harlem, with so many streets that a learned arithmetician would be needed to number them: a district which, at the first call of spring, becomes vocal with children on door steps and venders of every vegetable in every language.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "In this district, too, you hear strange trumpets blow, announcing knife and scissors grinders, and strange bells ringing from strings suspended across carts, whose merchandise is bottles and old newspapers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Well, it was just then that a young poet, living in one of those highly arithmetical streets, was wondering, as all the sad spring murmur came to his ears, how he could possibly buy a rose for the bosom of his sweetheart, with whom he was to dance that night at a local ball. Everything he had in the world had gone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "He had sold everything-except his poems.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "All his precious books had gone, sad one by one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Little paintings that once made his walls seem like the Louvre had gone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "All his old silver spoons and all the little intaglios he loved so well, and yes! he had even sold the old copper chest of the Renaissance, all studded nails, with three locks, in which ... well, all had gone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Only, where was that rose for the bosom of his sweetheart-where was it growing?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Where and how was it to be bought?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Just as he was at his wit's end, he heard a cry through the window.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "It had meant nothing to him before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Now-strange as it may sound-it meant a rose!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "He had an old dress suit in his wardrobe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Perhaps that would buy a rose! So, leaning through the window, he called down to the voice to \"come up.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "The gentleman from Palestine came up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "It would be easy to describe the contempt with which he surveyed the distinguished though somewhat ancient garments thus offered to him-in exchange for a rose!--how he affected to examine linings and seams, knowing all the time the distinguished tailor that had made them, and what a bargain he was about to drive.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Of course, they weren't, well ... really ... practically ... they weren't worth buying....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "The poet wondered a moment about the cost of a rose.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "\"Are they worth the price of a rose?\" he asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "The gentleman from Palestine didn't, of course, understand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "\"You see,\" said he, finally; \"I'd like to give you more, but you know how it is ... look at these linings and buttonholes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Honestly, I don't really care about them at all-but-really a dollar and a half is the best I can do on them....\" And he eyed the poet's clothes with contempt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "\"A dollar seventy five,\" said the poet, standing firm.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "\"All right,\" at last said the gentleman from Palestine, \"but I don't see where I am to make any profit; however-\" And he handed out the small, dirty money.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "Then the poet bowed him out gently, saying in his heart:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "\"Now I can buy my rose!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "When the Palestinian dealer in old dress suits went home-after sadly leaving behind him that dollar seventy five-he made an astonishing discovery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "In the necessary process of re examining the \"goods,\" something fell out of one of the pockets, something the poet, after his nature, had quite forgotten.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "The old clothes man, now a publisher, picked them up from the floor and gazed at them in delight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "The poet, in his grandiose carelessness, had forgotten to empty his pockets of various old dreams!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_114962_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6535/114962/6535_114962_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6535",
        "content": "He read on and read on, and laughed and cried-such a curious treasure trove, such an odd medley of fairy tales and fables and poems had fallen out of the poet's pocket-and it was only later that the thought came to him that he might change from an old clothes man into a publisher of dreams.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6535_66371_000005_000001",
